: \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brooks, who recently won the prestigious Hodge Trophy as the nation's top collegiate wrestler, has been chasing his dream for 19 years.\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 326, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stream NBC4 newscasts for free right here, right now.\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When his dad asked him what he wanted to be, he said he wanted to be the greatest of all time,\\\" Brooks' mom, Ranelle Boyd, said.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brooks is already on his way.\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 543, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He boasted an impressive 163-2 record at North Hagerstown High School before moving on to Penn State University, where he won four national titles.\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 634, \"end\": 655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"score\": 0.9995335154420844, \"rank\": 0.0003252383359195612, \"text\": \"Penn State University\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boyd recalls her first time watching him wrestle: \\\"I did not know he was winning because I did not understand the points, so I am crying because I just see his opponent being really physical with him.\\\"\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then, Boyd has become well-versed in wrestling rules, which will be handy as she watches her son compete in Paris.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1010, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999550064025899, \"rank\": 4.499562203811149e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never would have imagined that I, Ranelle Boyd, would have an Olympian,\\\" Boyd said.\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999991643618468, \"rank\": 6.715657570180289e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's always going to be my baby boy, not the Olympian, not the 24-year-old man.\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1151, \"end\": 1159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999991643618468, \"rank\": 6.715657570180289e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's my baby.\\\"\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Washington, D.C., Maryland and Virginia local news, events and information  Concerns arose when she heard about the cardboard beds and lack of air conditioning in the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1204, \"end\": 1220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_metropolitan_area\", \"score\": 0.956253280190278, \"rank\": 0.0457417794681339, \"text\": \"Washington, D.C.\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_metropolitan_area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_metropolitan_area\"}, {\"begin\": 1222, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland_Terrapins_football\", \"score\": 0.520793257560985, \"rank\": 0.624897474307244, \"text\": \"Maryland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland_Terrapins_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland_Terrapins_football\"}, {\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia\", \"score\": 0.9846383326152952, \"rank\": 0.009276345718099965, \"text\": \"Virginia\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia\"}, {\"begin\": 1371, \"end\": 1386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999939070676, \"rank\": 6.092998468242545e-09, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Team USA wrestler Kyle Snyder said that Brooks came prepared.\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1397, \"end\": 1405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9998980811419197, \"rank\": 6.49967446613095e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Snyder_(wrestler)\", \"score\": 0.8442804931544928, \"rank\": 0.18242790073777754, \"text\": \"Kyle Snyder\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Snyder_(wrestler)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Snyder_(wrestler)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I told him we are going to get a lot of gear here, so do not pack much.\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He still ended up with a 123-pound bag,\\\" Snyder said.\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1574, \"end\": 1580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.9999550928434471, \"rank\": 2.949386286094448e-05, \"text\": \"Snyder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], 