f hard work.\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1980, \"end\": 1985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron\", \"score\": 0.8077719957505703, \"rank\": 0.12552933312628087, \"text\": \"Aaron\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron\"}]}]}"